{"tid":1082694,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網友翻出臧芮軒與台北市政府副發言人「學姐」撞臉   高呼「2位都是美人胚子啊！」","createTime":"2019-03-29T06:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T13:09:54.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b0a8e6712c1566c081e9433374efcabe22d5ad3d","tid":1082694,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:24:45.000Z","msg":"北市政府副發言人「學姐」黃瀞瑩，一舉一動都是網路關注焦點，近來更是議題不斷，有「爆廢公社」的網友們發現，覺得「學姐」跟某位台灣藝人長相神似！原來指的是演出八點檔、偶像劇的前正妹主播臧芮軒，「撞臉說」引起不少討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/03/28/99/6104894.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F03%2F28%2F99%2F6104894.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=cf4bf7c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n臧芮軒清新可人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/03/28/99/6104899.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F03%2F28%2F99%2F6104899.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=32c3c8c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「學姐」黃瀞瑩（右）是柯文哲得力助手。<br />\n<br />\n臧芮軒原本是udn主播，演藝圈後演出「甘味人生」、「一家人」，近期作品為偶像劇「艾蜜麗的五件事」，亮麗的外型和演出都受到好評，培養不少忠實鐵粉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://admin.eladies.sina.com.tw/news_images/img_tw/sina_fashion/2017/0718/15003741619682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fadmin.eladies.sina.com.tw%2Fnews_images%2Fimg_tw%2Fsina_fashion%2F2017%2F0718%2F15003741619682.jpg&h=37534a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友紛紛大讚二人「雙美合壁」。<br />\n<br />\n對於網友「學姐撞臉說」，臧芮軒透過臉書表示是託學姐的福，她說：「我覺得學姐比較正！」。粉絲則大讚：「2位都是美人胚子啊！」、「學姐就是你姊姊對吧！」、「有像喔！」、「根本雙美」。"},{"pid":"5175d67e38c9e685eec0c302f7caa261f8dbb0b7","tid":1082694,"uid":167118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"邊撚度似"},{"pid":"48da6a59f7ed0df1bb7dae0ed33e34d5b8f53022","tid":1082694,"uid":44153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最尾果張係新木優子嚟？"},{"pid":"37d112a11b7e8b9fd49a5445d41486007e6eafe1","tid":1082694,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"邊撚度美"},{"pid":"1786e92cf2ba987819b673359273f5ca64bc7bcc","tid":1082694,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/224/5c93ab6e73cda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F224%2F5c93ab6e73cda.jpg&h=8798f880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpc9XJ1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpc9XJ1F.jpg&h=dedad3f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc28d21494dce8687d35d3e99df8e4edae14de4","tid":1082694,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"咁都叫美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣無醜婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecd4e1d889d1086fe69be83d8d93f3f4c5cd64d","tid":1082694,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9966dd0561348598a203b73185286058278841b",